{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2021/05/11/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learning LaTeX</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://learnlatex.GitHub.io/\">learnlatex.GitHub.io</a> - Browser-based LaTeX tutorial.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Distributions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tug.org/mactex/\">MacTeX</a> - Most common LaTeX distribution for macOS, basically TeXLive with some Mac-specific tools added. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Distributions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.tug.org/texlive/\">TeX Live</a> - Most common LaTeX distribution for Unix-like operating systems, including GNU/Linux. Also works on Windows. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Distributions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://miktex.org\">MikTeX</a> - Most common LaTeX distribution for Windows (only). <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.tug.org/applications/pdftex/\">pdfTeX</a> - TeX compiler that produces PDF files immediately instead of DVI files (nowadays, this is the standard compiler for many users). <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://xetex.sourceforge.net\">XeTeX</a> - TeX compiler that provides better unicode and font support than TeX/pdfTeX (i.e. you can use the  fonts of your operating system instead of only TeX fonts). <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.luatex.org\">LuaTeX</a> - (La)TeX compiler that supports Lua code for scripting and has improved unicode and font support than standard TeX/pdfTeX. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tectonic-typesetting.GitHub.io/en-US/\">tectonic</a> - Modern, self contained (La)TeX compiler powered by XeTeX and TeXLive. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2><h3>LaTeX formulas on the web</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.mathjax.org\">MathJaX</a> - JavaScript engine to render mathematical formulas on the web. The outcome looks really slick. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2><h3>LaTeX formulas on the web</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://khan.GitHub.io/KaTeX/\">KaTeX</a> - KaTeX is a math rendering library made by Khan Academy focusing on fast load times. All output is processed as plain HTML instead of fixed images. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Engines</h2><h3>LaTeX formulas on the web</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://franklinjl.org/\">Franklin.jl</a> - Static site generator with KaTeX support, code evaluation, LaTeX-like commands and optional pre-rendering, in Julia. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://kile.sourceforge.io\">Kile</a> - Great LaTeX editor originally from the Linux/KDE community. It runs fine on Windows and macOS as well. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.winedt.com\">WinEdt</a> - The LaTeX editor many people swear by. Only for <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\">.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.texniccenter.org\">TeXnicCenter</a> - Quite old but free and decent editor for LaTeX. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.lyx.org\">LyX</a> - Cross-platform WYSIWYM editor that uses LaTeX behind the scenes to render documents. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://pages.uoregon.edu/koch/texshop/\">TeXShop</a> - No-nonsense editor for LaTeX documents which is included in MacTeX. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.tug.org/texworks/\">TeXWorks</a> - No-nonsense editor for LaTeX code, modeled after TeXShop, but this one is cross-platform. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.inlage.com/home\">Inlage</a> - Commercial LaTeX editor with handwritten formula recognition, Excel importing and more nifty features. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>LaTeX-focused</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.texpadapp.com\">Texpad</a> - Commercial LaTeX editor for macOS and iOS, with excellent features (document overview, synchronised PDF display, autocompletion, sync across devices, etc.) that never get in the way of writing. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>General purpose text editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://atom.io\">Atom</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/mehcode/awesome-atom\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Atom\"></a> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://atom.io/packages/latextools\">LaTeXTools</a> - Atom port of the Sublime Text package of the same name. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>General purpose text editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a>  <a href=\"https://github.com/emacs-tw/awesome-emacs\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Emacs\"></a> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/auctex/\">AucTeX</a> - Emacs plugin for LaTeX that also shows a preview of equations and figures. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/auctex/reftex\">RefTeX</a> - Emacs plugin for LaTeX that adds support for labels, references, and citations. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>General purpose text editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.vim.org\">Vim</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/mhinz/vim-galore\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Vim\"></a> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://vim-latex.sourceforge.net\">Vim-LaTeX</a> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/xuhdev/vim-latex-live-preview\">LaTeX Live Preview</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/xuhdev/vim-latex-live-preview\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">660</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":660,\"repo\":\"xuhdev/vim-latex-live-preview\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Instantly previews your LaTeX document. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/lervag/vimtex\">vimtex</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/lervag/vimtex\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.2k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3211,\"repo\":\"lervag/vimtex\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Modern vim plugin for editing LaTeX files. Has a variety of features including live preview and forward search. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>General purpose text editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\">VS Code</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/viatsko/awesome-vscode\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"VS Code\"></a> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/James-Yu/LaTeX-Workshop\">LaTeX Workshop</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/James-Yu/LaTeX-Workshop\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7.5k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":7465,\"repo\":\"James-Yu/LaTeX-Workshop\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - LaTeX extension for Visual Studio Code <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Editors</h2><h3>Online editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zohooo.GitHub.io/jaxedit/\">JaxEdit</a> - Online LaTeX editor with Live Preview and nice presentation mode.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Bibliography tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.jabref.org\">JabRef</a> - Very powerful cross-platform (Java) bibtex editor. The GUI looks quite dated, though. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Bibliography tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://bibdesk.sourceforge.net\">Bibdesk</a> - Great bibliography editor for <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\">.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Bibliography tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.zotero.org\">Zotero</a> - Reference manager for your browser that also exports to bibtex and integrates with many LaTeX editors. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <a href=\"https://github.com/zotero/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></a></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Bibliography tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.mendeley.com\">Mendeley</a> - Both an app and cloud client to manage your references and PDFs. Can sync out to a bibtex file for your LaTeX workflow. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Bibliography tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/nschloe/betterbib\">betterbib</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nschloe/betterbib\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">392</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":392,\"repo\":\"nschloe/betterbib\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Command-line utility for improving your BibTeX files. Fetches information from online sources. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Build Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.ctan.org/pkg/arara\">Arara</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/cereda/arara\">GitHub repo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/cereda/arara\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">311</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":311,\"repo\":\"cereda/arara\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->) - Simple tool that allows you to specify which tools to call inside your document and it can be extended quite easily. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Build Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.ctan.org/pkg/latexmk\">latexmk</a> - Build tool that is the commonly used by many LaTeX editors (LaTeXing, TeXShop, etc.) to build your LaTeX files. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Build Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/alejandrogallo/latex-makefile\">latex-makefile</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/alejandrogallo/latex-makefile\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">10</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":10,\"repo\":\"alejandrogallo/latex-makefile\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - <code>Makefile</code> based build tool that attempts to be as general and lightweight as possible. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pandoc.org\">Pandoc</a> - This program converts almost any document format (LaTeX, DOC, markdown, etc.) to almost any other format. A great tool to aid workflows where multiple formats are used. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.chachatelier.fr/latexit/\">LaTeXiT</a> - LaTeXit is an equation editor that makes it easy to drag-and-drop rendered equations (as PDF, PNG, etc.) into your non-LaTeX documents on the Mac. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://klatexformula.sourceforge.io\">KLaTeXFormula</a> - Cross-platform alternative for LaTeXit. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://equalx.sourceforge.net\">EqualX</a> - Graphical LaTeX formula editor. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://baruch.ev-en.org/proj/chktex/\">ChkTeX</a> - Linter / code checker for LaTeX documents. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://latexeqedit.sourceforge.net/index.php\">LaTeXEqEdit</a> - LaTeX formula editor for Windows. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.thrysoee.dk/laeqed/\">Laeqed</a> - Crossplatform LaTeX formula to PNG convertor. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc. Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/nschloe/blacktex\">blacktex</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nschloe/blacktex\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">56</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":56,\"repo\":\"nschloe/blacktex\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Command-line tool that replaces commonly occurring LaTeX anti-patterns and cleans up your files. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>LaTeX-compatible GUI tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.tikzedt.org\">TikzEdt</a> (also: <a href=\"https://github.com/hchapman/tikzedt\">GitHub repo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hchapman/tikzedt\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">8</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":8,\"repo\":\"hchapman/tikzedt\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->) - WYSIWYG and text-based editor for TikZ pictures. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>LaTeX-compatible GUI tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fredokun/TikZ-Editor\">TikZ-Editor</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fredokun/TikZ-Editor\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">151</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":151,\"repo\":\"fredokun/TikZ-Editor\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Live-previewing editor for TikZ figures. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>LaTeX-compatible GUI tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://ipe.otfried.org\">IPE</a> - Drawing tool that integrates well with LaTeX commands and documents. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>LaTeX-compatible GUI tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.geogebra.org/cms/\">GeoGebra</a> - Cross-platform geometry tool with output to TikZ. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>LaTeX-compatible GUI tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wiki.gnome.org/Apps/Dia\">Dia</a> - Cross-platform diagramming tool that can export to PSTricks and MetaPost code. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T20:48:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX","categoryHTML":"<h2>LaTeX-compatible GUI tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tikzit.GitHub.io\">TikZiT</a> - GUI tool for creating graphs and string diagrams using PGF/TikZ. <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/windows.svg\" alt=\"windows\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/linux.svg\" alt=\"linux\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/apple.svg\" alt=\"mac\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/egeerardyn/awesome-LaTeX/700138fe725574e1741f148df6d1f77a8aa07eee/fig/foss.svg\" alt=\"foss\"></li>","updatedA